exercise and Ehrlich's diet,

02:24.440 --> 02:26.240
I look better, I feel better.

02:26.240 --> 02:27.960
Who's leading rounds for Westphall?

02:27.960 --> 02:29.000
Craig.

02:29.000 --> 02:31.200
