wasn't that long ago.

03:41.160 --> 03:43.800
All right, Axelrod, your first case.

03:43.800 --> 03:45.680
Uh, Worzoger, Harriet.

03:45.680 --> 03:49.320
Where the hell have you been?
Rounds start on time, mister.

03:49.320 --> 03:51.480
I was...
But I thought we...

03:51.480 --> 03:52.680
I went to...

03:52.680 --> 03:56.680
           Oh, shut up!

03:57.760 --> 04:01.760
Tommy and I picked these
marigolds before school.

04:02.400 --> 04:03.440
Here's your mail.

04:03.440 --> 04:04.560
Thank you.

04:04.560 --> 04:07.600
Your daughter called.
She's coming tomorrow.

04:07.600 --> 04:08.920
Is she bringing Rick?

04:08.920 --> 04:09.960
Nope.

04:09.960 --> 04:13.160
Are you upset because she
went out west with Horace Greenbay?

04:13.160 --> 04:15.120
I am. It's not
                that she lied to me,

04:15.120 --> 04:16.839
it's just she
               left out the details.

04:16.839 --> 04:20.120
Dishonesty through omission -
a disease among young women.

04:20.120 --> 04:22.120
Maureen had a chronic case.

04:22.120 --> 04:24.040
What do you mean?

04:24.040 --> 04:27.240
Oh, I don't blame you for not
eating. Condemned prisoners

04:27.240 --> 04:29.520
get better slop.
From now on, I'm catering.

04:29.520 --> 04:30.640
Keep your voice down.

04:30.640 --> 04:33.080
If the dieticians hear you,
         I'll get letters.

04:33.080 --> 04:34.200
I own a restaurant.

04:34.200 --> 04:37.240
I have a personal aversion
 to seeing eggs treated that way.

04:37.240 --> 04:38.680
Those aren't eggs.

04:38.680 --> 04:41.000
Excuse us!

04:41.000 --> 04:45.000
I will stop back later with
a little low cuisine. Feel better.

04:45.200 --> 04:46.800
Who's she?

04:46.800 --> 04:48.080
His sister-in-law.

04:48.080 --> 04:51.080
All you've done for the last
two weeks is come in with these

04:51.080 --> 04:53.880
residents to poke at me.
  I'm not a geek in a sideshow.

04:53.880 --> 04:56.000
Don't be so selfish.
When do these slugs

04:56.000 --> 04:59.680
get to eyeball a tropical disease
in the middle of Boston Harbour?

04:59.680 --> 05:01.880
      Well, present the case.

05:01.880 --> 05:04.760
Patient's name is Westphall, Donald.

05:04.760 --> 05:06.560
White male, 55.

05:06.560 --> 05:09.360
         We know all that!

05:09.360 --> 05:13.360
Admitted two weeks ago after
syncopal episode with high fever.

05:13.640 --> 05:17.400
Physical exam was remarkable
   for palpable spleen.

05:17.400 --> 05:21.400
Peripheral blood smear showed
presence of falciparum malaria.

05:21.600 --> 05:25.600
Your crit's up. We could use a little
more improvement in renal function.

05:26.000 --> 05:28.040
Palpate the spleen for assessment.

05:28.040 --> 05:31.080
Well, I've never palpated
another doctor before.

05:31.080 --> 05:35.080
   What's the difference? Do it!

05:35.200 --> 05:38.680
Be gentle.

05:38.680 --> 05:40.000
Axelrod?

05:40.000 --> 05:40.440
Mm?

05:40.440 --> 05:42.760
Mm?
Under the clothes.

05:42.760 --> 05:46.200
So I guess you won't be
going back to the Cape soon!

05:46.200 --> 05:48.160
               I'm selling the house.

05:48.160 --> 05:52.160
After what happened to you,
I'd do the same thing.

05:54.840 --> 05:58.080
      Hello there, Mr Boyden.

05:58.080 --> 06:00.360
     Your evaluation, please.

06:00.360 --> 06:02.160
My sails are off.

06:02.160 --> 06:04.600
Might as well look at
            the doorknob growing out

06:04.600 --> 06:06.440
of my wrist instead of the samples.

06:06.440 --> 06:09.880
It appears to be a small ganglion
cyst on the wrist. A Bible node.

06:09.880 --> 06:10.960
Course of treatment?

06:10.960 --> 06:13.440
Doctors used to whack these
babies with a book,

06:13.440 --> 06:16.480
a Bible being the tool of choice.
I'd recommend local excision.

06:16.480 --> 06:17.400
Schedule surgery for Thursday.

06:17.400 --> 06:20.120
Schedule surgery for Thursday.
Hey, Caldwell, while we're there,

06:20.120 --> 06:22.280
do something about
     the shades over my eyes.

06:22.280 --> 06:24.480
Let's take care
of the cyst first, huh?

06:24.480 --> 06:26.360
Can you see through
that bandage?

06:26.360 --> 06:28.160
  This'll be off after tomorrow.

06:28.160 --> 06:30.040
If my vision
is in any way blurred,

06:30.040 --> 06:31.960
I'll have another
surgeon step in.

06:31.960 --> 06:33.400
What did happen to your face?

06:33.400 --> 06:37.400
Mailman bit me.

06:38.160 --> 06:39.480
Are you interested

06:39.480 --> 06:42.240
in two free tickets to hear
Chuck Cochrane speak tonight?

06:42.240 --> 06:42.680
The astronaut?

06:42.680 --> 06:43.800
The astronaut?
You've heard of him?

06:43.800 --> 06:46.960
He repaired the IPC satellite
on the last Shuttle mission.

06:46.960 --> 06:49.520
Hey, great!
Here. I was just gonna toss 'em.

06:49.520 --> 06:52.520
I've followed every mission
since the Mercury Project.

06:52.520 --> 06:54.440
I have models of all the rockets.

06:54.440 --> 06:55.880
I wanted to be an astronaut.

06:55.880 --> 06:56.320
You?!

06:56.320 --> 06:57.480
You?!
Yeah.

06:57.480 --> 07:01.400
What better job for a space cadet?

07:01.400 --> 07:03.160
            Will you jokers hurry up?

07:03.160 --> 07:04.920
     We're not on a Sierra Club hike.

07:04.920 --> 07:07.200
                Dr Fiscus, next case.

07:07.200 --> 07:10.760
Pru Dowler,
26, female, mentally retarded,

07:10.760 --> 07:14.480
held for observation after blunt
trauma to the abdomen yesterday

07:14.480 --> 07:17.760
when a bus load of disabled people
was hit by a drunk driver.

07:17.760 --> 07:21.760
Uh, vitals all stable,
hypertensive, BP's 156/94.

07:28.520 --> 07:29.760
Hello, Miss Dowler.

07:29.760 --> 07:31.640
My name's Pru.  Hi.

07:31.640 --> 07:34.040
Are you feeling better today?

07:34.040 --> 07:35.040
Uh-huh.

07:35.040 --> 07:36.560
Uh-huh.
Let me take a look at you.

07:36.560 --> 07:40.560
Just lie back.

07:43.240 --> 07:44.800
          Pretty picture.

07:44.800 --> 07:46.640
Wanna play?

07:46.640 --> 07:47.440
           Who are you?

07:47.440 --> 07:49.520
           Who are you?
Buddy.

07:49.520 --> 07:51.920
One of the other disabled
people from the crash.

07:51.920 --> 07:55.920
Can't you see we're
performing an examination here?

07:55.960 --> 07:59.840
Oh.

07:59.840 --> 08:00.960
I had a cat.

08:00.960 --> 08:03.240
Does she have a history
of hypertension?

08:03.240 --> 08:06.200
She's now on three
anti-hypertensives with control.

08:06.200 --> 08:07.640
Her name was Muffy.

08:07.640 --> 08:11.000
Mm-hm.
OK. So long, Pru.

08:11.000 --> 08:13.160
Internal medicine -
all talk, no action.

08:13.160 --> 08:15.400
Can I kiss you goodbye?

08:15.400 --> 08:19.400
Uh, Fiscus, take care
of that, will you?

08:25.160 --> 08:25.720
&lt; Bye.

08:25.720 --> 08:28.000
&lt; Bye.
Bye.

08:28.000 --> 08:31.440
I can't believe it, a rotation
I've been dreading all these months

08:31.440 --> 08:33.039
     has turned into a dream.

08:33.039 --> 08:34.159
Don't get too happy.

08:34.159 --> 08:35.919
Most of the time
I'll be on vacation.

08:35.919 --> 08:37.120
Most of the time
I'll be on vacation.
                      Well, delay it.

08:37.120 --> 08:38.520
I haven't had time off

08:38.520 --> 08:41.039
since the ex and I
went on our honeymoon.

08:41.039 --> 08:44.400
It's a week of fishing
in the Gulf of Mexico.

08:44.400 --> 08:46.800
I don't like being back
here any more than you do.

08:46.800 --> 08:50.320
Terri, the tour's here.

08:50.320 --> 08:53.240
Welcome to the foetus factory.

08:53.240 --> 08:54.840
Here you go, Ken.

08:54.840 --> 08:58.760
By this point, the jar and I
should announce our engagement!

08:58.760 --> 09:02.760
Dr Chandler, would you fill
everyone in on the case?

09:02.960 --> 09:06.240
Yes, um, Valere, Terri,
33-year-old white female,

09:06.240 --> 09:08.960
blocked Fallopian tubes
causing infertility.

09:08.960 --> 09:12.960
She was placed on HMG in preparation
for in-vitro fertilisation.

09:13.560 --> 09:16.800
Saw egg follicles in ultrasound
of stimulated ovulation prior

09:16.800 --> 09:18.600
     to ovum harvest tomorrow.

09:18.600 --> 09:22.240
It's harvest time! The leaves
are turning, and so's my stomach.

09:22.240 --> 09:26.240
If you'll excuse me, duty calls.

09:27.520 --> 09:30.280
What happened to the tall,
gawky resident?

09:30.280 --> 09:34.280
Dr Morrison.
He finished his rotation. &gt;

09:34.720 --> 09:35.880
          Chest is clear.

09:35.880 --> 09:37.880
We've been guinea
pigs for that long?

09:37.880 --> 09:41.320
Ken and I must be underwriting
St Eligius' budget by now.

09:41.320 --> 09:44.040
But this time I've got
    a feeling it's gonna work.

09:44.040 --> 09:45.760
                   Heart sounds fine.

09:45.760 --> 09:48.800
Terri, it's still a crap shoot.

09:48.800 --> 09:49.920
