16:03.840 --> 16:06.400
So what do I do?
Let emergency C-sections

16:06.400 --> 16:08.000
wait in the hall.

16:08.000 --> 16:09.800
I don't know what the answer is.

16:09.800 --> 16:12.520
More referrals, longer
clinic hours, I don't know.

16:12.520 --> 16:15.880
Don't these bozos have anything
better to do than kick up trouble?

16:15.880 --> 16:18.680
This is serious, Bob.
If both of you don't

16:18.680 --> 16:22.680
